                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18261026-189-off1054 t18261026-189-cd1055"></join>, 1 pair of breeches, value 14s.; 1 shawl, value 15s.; 6 handkerchiefs, value 6s.; 1 and cap, value 3s.; 1 waistcoat, value 4s.; 1 basket, value 6d.; 1 half-crown, and fourpence, in copper monies
